{"tid":715770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想改廁所門位，裝修巴打入","createTime":"2018-06-24T17:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T01:14:22.000Z","uid":172701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96ab7f51c38edeca6dd61ba06fa52879159e7f10","tid":715770,"uid":172701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:45:16.000Z","msg":"想裝修過間屋<br />\n其中一個諗法係將廁所嘅門向右手邊入一格<br />\n等出面道牆可以用黎放到電視櫃<br />\n但係就變左要拆門拆牆改細個企缸<br />\n企缸個水龍頭本身係門個邊，要改返去裡面<br />\n門諗住改為趟門<br />\n同埋要將啲電線個啲拉返去個邊<br />\n有冇有經驗嘅巴打知道咁樣整要幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/013251_f330fedab063cebd0490e5c78a53b5c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F013251_f330fedab063cebd0490e5c78a53b5c7.jpg&h=d3129701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖，長2.15m闊1.38m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30ad841450c59b183d760d12c3333d0afa7f065","tid":715770,"uid":172701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:14:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}